  "3318140": {
    "name": "Workaholic Simulator: Leaving the Dream",
    "steam_appid": 3318140,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318140/extras/db0f8398a5a160f9e3b9a14749144ee9.poster.avif?t=1770027425\" width=693 height=261 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318140/extras/db0f8398a5a160f9e3b9a14749144ee9.webm?t=1770027425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >陌生而熟悉的恐怖</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >工作狂模拟器 离开梦想》通过每个人都必须忍受的最可怕的经历--工作，探索了当代世界的黑暗。如果你是一名在职成年人，你可能会发现一些你每天都要面对的主题，但这款游戏将这一众所周知的环境加以扭曲，使其成为一种超现实的体验。你将永远不会以同样的方式看待自己的工作！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318140/extras/7734fc181618192963feaddd5614586b.poster.avif?t=1770027425\" width=693 height=261 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318140/extras/7734fc181618192963feaddd5614586b.webm?t=1770027425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >身临其境的体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过精心打造的环境、定制的音效设计和音乐，沉浸在这个令人不寒而栗的故事中。白天过着普通工人的生活，进入梦乡......但即使进入梦乡也无法逃避工作，因为噩梦般的实体会在梦中追杀你，你将不得不在更大的压力下完成工作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318140/extras/4f0d17c9cdddadf82ce35831aa6ad7b8.poster.avif?t=1770027425\" width=693 height=261 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318140/extras/4f0d17c9cdddadf82ce35831aa6ad7b8.webm?t=1770027425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >噩梦还是现实？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你永远无法预料在这些幻觉走廊和边缘走廊中会发现什么。当你走过这些异化空间时，谁知道每个角落背后都潜藏着什么？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中没有声音，几乎没有文字，因此游戏的故事将由您自己来揭开。所有的叙述都是通过情绪和环境细节来完成的。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你必须做好准备，因为只有你的智慧和敏捷的思维才能让你逃离这个虚无缥缈的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318140/extras/be3b4a509ca47e9f90983228ef5489c5.poster.avif?t=1770027425\" width=693 height=261 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318140/extras/be3b4a509ca47e9f90983228ef5489c5.webm?t=1770027425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >神秘与秘密</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的不同结局会让最善于观察、最好奇的玩家大饱眼福。除了要通过连线和填空来解开所有谜团外，还有很多秘密等着您去挖掘。请时刻保持警惕，但不要忘了，你永远不会是真正的一个人...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318140/extras/9872acaad95c50b53f939a624f1a1ad0.poster.avif?t=1770027425\" width=693 height=261 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318140/extras/9872acaad95c50b53f939a624f1a1ad0.webm?t=1770027425\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
